                        <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
                        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                        <p>To provide quality agricultural services, promote sustainable farming practices, and enhance the socio-economic status of farmers through innovative programs, technical assistance, and efficient resource management.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card-custom">
                        <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
                        <h3>Our Vision</h3>
                        <p>A progressive and self-sufficient agricultural community in Bulalacao where farmers are empowered, food security is achieved, and sustainable development is realized for all.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Core Values -->
